<!-- /wp:table -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2><a>When to see a doctor</a></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>It can be difficult to know if you have trouble hearing. Sometimes, it’s your friends and family who notice first. If people frequently tell you that you ask them to repeat themselves or you have the TV on too loud, it may be worth talking with a doctor.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Similarly, if you find that your hearing isn’t what it used to be and you have trouble following conversations in loud spaces or on the phone, you may need to get your hearing checked.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Why does it matter? Hearing loss may be treatable, and in some cases, hearing issues can be linked to an underlying medical cause that requires attention.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2><a>Frequently asked questions about Miracle-Ear</a></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3>Is Miracle-Ear a reputable brand?</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Miracle-Ear has been around for 73 years and has an A- BBB rating. Customer reviews are mixed, but many say the customer service is top-notch.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3>Who manufactures Miracle-Ear?</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The Italian company Amplifon makes Miracle-Ear hearing aids.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3>Is Miracle-Ear one of the best hearing aids on the market in 2022?</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Miracle-Ear is a popular hearing aid brand, but the best option for you depends on your needs and type of hearing loss.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2><a>Takeaway</a></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Miracle-Ear is a reputable hearing aid provider with more than 1,000 locations across the United States. You can make an appointment online.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>If you decide to get a hearing aid from Miracle-Ear, the device comes with a lifetime aftercare package.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

